item.description:
Join us for our kickoff event as we share our vision for the North of Boston Chapter and explain how being a member of Dare To Be Phenomenal will enhance your life. This is such an exciting time to be an entrepreneur and we look forward to helping you turn your passions into prosperity!

Inspiring women to live more passionate, purposeful and prosperous lives!
item.how_to_find_us: I will be waiting for you in the foyer area!
